result.notes:
Capital for Enterprise Limited is now part of Britis Business Bank. Operations and Staff were transferred from 1 October 2013. No additional data will be published for this organisation. 
This data has been produced in line with the requirements of the Transparency Agenda.  It shows the transactional spend of Capital for Enterprise Ltd which are equal to or more than £500 in value purchased using Government Procurement Cards for the period April 2013 - March 2014. Please consult the Department for Business, Innovation and Skills (BIS) for government procurement card spend after this date.
Capital for Enterprise Limited (CfEL) was the government’s main delivery agency for financial interventions for small and medium sized enterprises.
